title: Cartems Donuterie
description: Doughnut shop in downtown. Offers a daily vegan earl grey doughnut, as well as rotating selection of other vegan flavors. Also has gluten free, coffee and tea. Modern, upbeat atmosphere.
venueHours: Mon 8:00am-8:00pm, Tue 8:00am-6:00pm, Wed-Thu 8:00am-8:00pm, Fri 8:00am-10:00pm, Sat 11:00am-10:00am, Sun 11:00am-6:00pm
